{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f836a37673","title":"路过济南在火车上听取汇报时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f351fec77a","index":0,"year":1965,"month":11,"day":null,"articleId":"f836a37673"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"c62063b269","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1965年11月，毛泽东去华东路过济南，在火车上，有关领导向毛泽东汇报工作。这是毛泽东在听取报告时的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3758f48266","type":"title","text":"路过济南在火车上听取汇报时的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673"},{"id":"c62063b269","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东：你们有没有钢","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673"},{"id":"8fda46c48c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：准备搞吨，将来再发展到口万吨。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673"},{"id":"7896867429","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：哦，搞口口口吨，那好。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673"},{"id":"0ef841cb21","type":"paragraph","text":"我对这一条比较积极，我是支持地方的。各省总要有个口方吨的钢铁厂，能制造机器，制造武器。我不怕你们造反，我自己也是造反的，造了多少次反，袁世凯当皇帝逼出了个蔡锣造反。如果中央出了军阀，出了修正主义，你们就可以造反。但是你们不能随便造反，不能造马列主义的反，否则你们就会吃亏，会成为修正主义。一个省也造不起反来。一个省搞点钢！搞口万吨左右的钢铁厂，一翻口万吨，再一翻口口万吨，再一翻口口万吨。但是要有条件。没有条件就不能炼钢","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673"}],"page":{"id":"ae10b762d6","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"f836a37673","start":246,"end":246}}}},"__N_SSG":true}